I had announced it in the Announcements thread, though I hadn't named it. I posted this before leaving the house for a couple of hours, and forgot to edit the index page. I hadn't posted links to the individual iterations myself because I was afraid it would damage the immersion, but if it's in demand, thanks Troy for that one.

The reason for the %%title%% thing being in there isn't even to give a sense of added threat; it's more to add to a sense that should build up toward the end that this thing is right where it wants to be, doing exactly what it wants to be doing. That's how it redacted the section of its own containment document discussing how to destroy it in every iteration; it's not contained so much as it is vacationing on Foundation servers.







